#

Creamy Chicken Pasta Salad

25 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Fat

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyQuickHealthy

Description

A delightful blend of tender chicken, fresh vegetables, and creamy dressing, perfect for a light lunch or dinner!

Ingredients

  • pasta (fusilli or rotini): 2 cups
  • cooked chicken breast, diced: 1 cup
  • cherry tomatoes, halved: 1 cup
  • cucumber, diced: 1 cup
  • red bell pepper, diced: 1/2 cup
  • sweet corn, drained: 1/2 cup
  • mayonnaise: 1/4 cup
  • greek yogurt: 1/4 cup
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • dried oregano: 1 teaspoon
